race.comment: YESNOVA (5) snagged back from the draw on resumption when a fast finishing third over 1200m at Gosford. Gets a similar set-up for this and will be charging late. G'DAY AUSBRED (6) sound debut before struggling at the 1500m when sixth at Kembla Grange. Kept fresh and will hold a forward position. Each way. ARIZONA LONER (1) not that far away on debut at the big odds when a close-up seventh over 1250m at Canterbury. Will drift back and be saved for one crack at them. SO REBELLIOUS (8) comes here with a fitness edge over most of these and can get cover from the draw. Improver. LETHAL LOVE (11) had no luck from the wide draw at latest over 1200m at Gosford. Maps well with senior rider engaged.
